OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,F'It was carnage': A widow speaks of
OL,7,Fher horrific experience with NHS
OL,8,Fcorridor care, reports ITV News Health
OL,9,FCorrespondent Rebecca Barry
OL,11,FCoroners have issued dozens of formal
OL,12,Fwarnings about the deadly risks of
OL,13,F'corridor care' and hospital
OL,14,Fovercrowding in England in recent
OL,15,Fyears, ITV News can reveal.
OL,17,FOne woman whose husband spent 36 hours
OL,18,Fin the "carnage" of an A&E corridor,
OL,19,Fwhile suffering fatal swelling of the
OL,20,Fbrain, told us the experience has left
OL,21,Fher feeling "desperate and helpless".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
