OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FThe health secretary has admitted that
OL,7,Fdelivering on his promise to eradicate
OL,8,F'corridor care' by 2029 will not be an
OL,9,F"overnight fix".
OL,11,FResearch by ITV News has found that
OL,12,Fsince 2020, the government and
OL,13,Fhospital trusts have received 27
OL,14,Fformal documents from coroners calling
OL,15,Ffor action to prevent future deaths
OL,16,Flinked to a lack of hospital beds.
OL,18,FBut over that period, long waits in
OL,19,Femergency departments have soared.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
