OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FIn January 2020, around 2,800 patients
OL,7,Fin England waited more than 12 hours
OL,8,Fin A&E to get a hospital bed.
OL,10,FBy January this year, that figure had
OL,11,Frocketed to more than 70,000 - the
OL,12,Fhighest on record.
OL,14,FResearch by NHS England shows the
OL,15,Fnumber of patients waiting on a
OL,16,Ftrolley for more than 12 hours from
OL,17,Fdecision to admit to admission, by
OL,18,Fyear. The graph shows the figure rose
OL,19,Ffrom 1,621 in February 2020 to 54,649
OL,20,Fin February 2026
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
