CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FTom Frith, 66, from Cheshire, was
OL,7,Frushed to the A&E department at
OL,8,FLeighton Hospital in June 2025,
OL,9,Fsuffering with a temperature,
OL,10,Fconfusion and struggling with his
OL,11,Fspeech.
OL,13,F"It was carnage - bodies everywhere
OL,14,Fand nurses running around," Tom's
OL,15,Fwife, Julia Chard, told ITV News.
OL,17,FTom was left in a corridor for 36
OL,18,Fhours, undiagnosed with a serious
OL,19,Fcondition called encephalitis, which
OL,20,Fcauses inflammation of the brain and
OL,21,Frequires urgent medical treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FHe was eventually diagnosed a week
OL,7,Fafter he first attended A&E, but due
OL,8,Fto the brain damage which had already
OL,9,Foccurred, Tom never recovered and died
OL,10,Fweeks later.
OL,12,F"No one should go through what Tom
OL,13,Fwent through," said Julia.
OL,15,F"He was fit, he had a life, he had a
OL,16,Fretirement plan - but all that's been
OL,17,Ftaken away. It's been ripped away and
OL,18,Fit's not fair."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,F"I have so many fabulous memories of
OL,7,FTom, which I can't see - because all I
OL,8,Fsee is him in that hospital."
OL,10,FITV News has found there have been
OL,11,Fnumerous official warnings about the
OL,12,Frisk of deaths linked to corridor care.
OL,14,FOur journalists searched through court
OL,15,Frecords since January 2020 and
OL,16,Fanalysed the paperwork filed by
OL,17,Fcoroners about hospital deaths in
OL,18,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
