OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FA Prevention of Future Deaths report
OL,7,Fis a formal document issued by a
OL,8,Fcoroner calling for action to improve
OL,9,Fsafety.
OL,11,FOver the last 6 years, ITV News found
OL,12,F27 of these reports relating to
OL,13,Fhospital corridor care, overcrowding
OL,14,For lack of beds.
OL,16,FThe reports were sent to the incumbent
OL,17,FHealth Secretary, NHS England and
OL,18,FHospital Trusts, urging them to act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FHere are some of the concerns coroners
OL,7,Fraised in their Prevention of Future
OL,8,FDeaths reports:
OL,10,FWhen asked if he accepts
OL,11,Fresponsibility for the failure to act
OL,12,Fupon these warnings, the Health
OL,13,FSecretary, Wes Streeting, told ITV
OL,14,FNews:
OL,16,F"It is my responsibility to sort this
OL,17,Fout.
OL,19,F"I committed to resolve corridor care
OL,20,Fover the course of this Parliament, by
OL,21,Fthe next general election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,F"There have been real improvements in
OL,7,Furgent and emergency care... We are
OL,8,Ffocused on improving corridor care,
OL,9,Fbut there is not going to be an
OL,10,Fovernight fix."
OL,12,FThe government has promised to start
OL,13,Fcollecting and publishing the data on
OL,14,Fcorridor care from May 2026, but some
OL,15,Fdoctors are worried that targets will
OL,16,Fobscure the truth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FDr Vicky Price, President of the
OL,7,FSociety of Acute Medicine, told ITV
OL,8,FNews she is concerned about
OL,9,F"gamification" and hospitals taking
OL,10,Fshortcuts to improve the data.
OL,12,F"I'm really worried that it will just
OL,13,Fbecome hidden - and then you've got
OL,14,Fhidden corridor that's just not as
OL,15,Fobvious. We've got to do this
OL,16,Fproperly, not too quickly and not just
OL,17,Fto make it look better but for it to
OL,18,Factually be better for patients."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
