OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,FJulia Chard has started a medical
OL,7,Fnegligence claim against the hospital
OL,8,Fthat treated her husband.
OL,10,FDr Clare Hammell, Chief Medical
OL,11,FOfficer and Deputy Chief Executive for
OL,12,FMid Cheshire Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,13,FTrust said: "Our thoughts are with Mr
OL,14,FFrith's family and loved ones, and we
OL,15,Fare very sorry for the distress they
OL,16,Fhave experienced.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,F"As a legal claim has now been issued,
OL,7,Fit would not be appropriate for the
OL,8,FTrust to comment on the specific
OL,9,Fcircumstances of Mr Frith's care or
OL,10,Fthe allegations that have been raised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
