FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,F"However, we take any concerns about
OL,7,Fpatient safety extremely seriously. We
OL,8,Fare cooperating fully with the legal
OL,9,Fprocess and are committed to making
OL,10,Fsure that any learning is carefully
OL,11,Fconsidered and shared in the right
OL,12,Fway. We continually review learning
OL,13,Ffrom incidents, complaints and claims
OL,14,Fto help us improve care, including
OL,15,Fongoing education and training for
OL,16,Fstaff to support the recognition and
OL,17,Fmanagement of rare but serious
OL,18,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
