PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774857949
OL,3,CDozens of coroner reports warn of
OL,4,Cdeadly risks of hospital corridor care
OL,6,F"We would like to reassure patients
OL,7,Fand the public that our staff work
OL,8,Ftirelessly to provide safe,
OL,9,Fcompassionate care, often in very
OL,10,Fchallenging circumstances, and we
OL,11,Fremain committed to learning and
OL,12,Fimprovement whenever concerns are
OL,13,Fraised."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
